{"tid":2492038,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蜑家女與菲臘親王在戰艦的日子 後代再入宮憶舊事","createTime":"2021-04-16T18:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T14:20:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5660c51efd72d0853056b56628c7dd648fe34afe","tid":2492038,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:46:12.000Z","msg":"上周五（9日）離世的菲臘親王與香港結緣甚深，他在二戰結束後乘坐驅逐艦HMS Whelp從日本抵港，協助香港重光。當時一群蜑家女工受聘修繕戰艦，與菲臘親王共事數個月。1959年菲臘親王再訪港時，特別邀請女工重聚。這班蜑家女工的後代李敏婷（Miriam）在2009年獲邀參觀白金漢宮，向菲臘親王提及長輩事蹟，當時年近90歲的親王仍記得女工的貢獻，「是的，我打仗的時候已經去過，那時有些很年輕的女工幫忙工作」。<br />\n<br />\n女工們除了補油漆，亦要負責織纜繩，軍艦就會提供餐飲。女工們與菲臘親王共事幾個月期間，對這位年輕的軍官印象甚佳，「（菲臘親王）成日請佢哋食糖呀，喺佢哋印象裏面，呢個係好好人軍官」。而戰艦離港前，菲臘親王特別記掛這班女工，「當時我啲長輩都有講過，佢臨走時候有特登問佢哋，有啲咩生活上需要」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210417/KI6ALNHSBZDALA55OQHJZYTCMU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210417%2FKI6ALNHSBZDALA55OQHJZYTCMU%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLw2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=11ac67b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210417%2FKI6ALNHSBZDALA55OQHJZYTCMU%2F&h=add200b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210417/KI6ALNHSBZDALA55OQHJZYTCMU/</a>"},{"pid":"675a55c686a0255c04fa174d9e354aa52e58c7c9","tid":2492038,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:59:02.000Z","msg":"好靚仔 <br />\n我都想食糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPon41T4DbSgV8PvAy3aFqgmiE3hX1uKxsDBpFsaJa78R?filename=vpjyR8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpjyR8.gif&h=8e9949e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75d1b2de30b579dc0f80ba64e7e6f6596d8036c9","tid":2492038,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T22:04:34.000Z","msg":"講到咁難忘唔通個閪識轉灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604e1d8c4d40dc0dd4a11e15d472f87936c91ef8","tid":2492038,"uid":258345,"like